OL,3,CThames Water discovers 312 storm
OL,4,Coverflows it didn't know it had
OL,6,FThe Brixton Storm Relief Sewer sits at
OL,7,Fthe foot of the MI6 building on the
OL,8,Fbanks of the river Thames.
OL,10,FLast year, this storm overflow spilt
OL,11,Fraw sewage into the river 130 times -
OL,12,Froughly one discharge every three days.
OL,14,FWater companies are permitted to dump
OL,15,Fsewage in "exceptional" circumstances.
OL,16,FStill, Ofwat has decided that Thames
OL,17,FWater has been doing so routinely
OL,18,Fsince 2017 because it has failed to
OL,19,Fproperly manage its network of sewers
OL,20,Fand treatment works.
