OL,6,FSome 39% of Thames Water's storm
OL,7,Foverflows "spill" more than 20 times a
OL,8,Fyear - the level the regulator
OL,9,Fconsiders to be excessive.
OL,11,FIn 2020, it was 49%.
OL,13,FOfwat fined three companies for sewage
OL,14,Fdischarges on Tuesday but Thames Water
OL,15,Fis the worst offender.
OL,17,FThe regulator's investigation said
OL,18,FThames Water has consistently failed
OL,19,Fto monitor, operate, maintain, repair
OL,20,Fand upgrade its assets.
