OL,6,FThe report highlights a lack of
OL,7,Finvestment but also a lack of care and
OL,8,Fcuriosity within the company -
OL,9,Fincluding at the board level.
OL,11,FThe investigation reveals that in
OL,12,F2022, Thames Water informed Ofwat it
OL,13,Fhad discovered 312 storm overflows it
OL,14,Fdidn't know existed and hadn't been
OL,15,Fmonitoring.
OL,17,FThames Water owns and operates 236
OL,18,Fwater treatment facilities, 157 are
OL,19,Fperforming so poorly that Thames
OL,20,FWaters considers them to be "sites of
OL,21,Fconcern".
