OL,6,FUntreated sewage is being discharged
OL,7,Fbecause these plants cannot cope with
OL,8,Fthe volume of wastewater they need to
OL,9,Fprocess.
OL,11,FMany of the plants are not running at
OL,12,Fcapacity because of what the regulator
OL,13,Fsays is a combination of human error
OL,14,Fand equipment that is either poorly
OL,15,Fmaintained or needs replacing.
