OL,6,FWater companies have faced a series of
OL,7,Fregulatory and legal actions since it
OL,8,Fbecame clear that they have been
OL,9,Freleasing unknown quantities of
OL,10,Fwastewater into national waterways,
OL,11,Fputting the environment and human
OL,12,Fhealth at risk.
OL,14,FThe Environment Agency is conducting
OL,15,Fits largest-ever criminal
OL,16,Finvestigation.
