OL,4,Coverflows it didn't know it had
OL,6,FLast month, the Supreme Court ruled
OL,7,Fthat individuals can seek compensation
OL,8,Ffor the sewage that has been released.
OL,10,FOfwat has fined Thames Water #104
OL,11,Fmillion and there may be more fines to
OL,12,Fcome. It has also proposed an
OL,13,F"enforcement" order which compels
OL,14,FThames Water to detail how it will
OL,15,Fimprove its network.
OL,17,FThames Water says it "takes this
OL,18,Fmatter very seriously", adding: "We
OL,19,Fregard all untreated discharges are
OL,20,Funacceptable, even when they are
OL,21,Fpermitted."
