OL,6,FThe company can appeal the fine and it
OL,7,Fneeds the money.
OL,9,FThe infrastructure is creaking and
OL,10,Fneeds upgrading.
OL,12,FLast month, Thames Water said it had
OL,13,Fenough cash to last until next May, by
OL,14,Fwhich time it needs to raise #750
OL,15,Fmillion from investors.
OL,17,FIf it can't, the company may be taken
OL,18,Finto "special administration", a form
OL,19,Fof temporary nationalisation.
