OL,6,FDespite the company's poor
OL,7,Fperformance, Chris Weston, who became
OL,8,Fchief executive in January, is set to
OL,9,Freceive a bonus of #195,000 for the
OL,10,Ffirst three months of this year.
OL,12,FOfwat is reviewing whether or not to
OL,13,Fintervene to prevent Thames Water from
OL,14,Fpaying the bonus using money raised
OL,15,Ffrom water bills.
